# 🔐 Roles and Permissions

| Role             | Description                                     |
|------------------|-------------------------------------------------|
| Admin            | Full access to all resources and management     |
| Manager          | Can manage data and users                       |
| UnitResponsible  | Can view data by department                     |
| ShiftLeader      | Can view and edit data of their assigned workers|
| User (Worker)    | Can submit entries and view own effectiveness   |

> Role restrictions are enforced via [Authorize] attributes and service logic.
